足以彌補過去多年虧損。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前該公司最大的股東為擁有49%股權的中國海航集團。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我真係恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954de97bc951e0e2ce7a34ee46b58574b5b6d866","tid":1556569,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JePh08U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJePh08U.jpg&h=e35cc0de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed3c3ac03e898bc896c026a491a543704037788d","tid":1556569,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:25:18.000Z","msg":"外國究竟明唔明同支那做生意係一件幾危險嘅事"},{"pid":"a98db85bfe5033c0177392fd74467304ad8f0d42","tid":1556569,"uid":42313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"比大陸公司揸旗都無好野，啲錢都比黨貪哂"}]}